{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_14_01_short",
  "title": "神崎莉央 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？\n私が恋愛ゲームのヒロインに？",
      "startTime": 1.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。今度のもし恋は『大人の恋愛』がテーマなので\nぜひ、莉央さんにお願いしたいそうです",
      "startTime": 9.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "大人の恋愛……それで年長組の私にオファーがきたのね\nでも、私との恋愛なんて需要があるのかしら？",
      "startTime": 18.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.7333332698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "需要とか言わないで下さい。莉央さんのファンは大勢\nいますから、中には恋愛したい人もきっといますよ",
      "startTime": 26.5666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2999999364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "「中には」とか「きっと」とか、一言余計よ",
      "startTime": 30.2999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.0999989192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、もし恋の魅力は恋のトキメキや青春のキラキラ\nでしょ？　私のイメージには合わないと思うけど",
      "startTime": 39.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。トキメキや青春とは馴染みがなくても\n莉央さんには莉央さんの良さがあります",
      "startTime": 47.1999989192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8333322525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから微妙に褒められてる気がしないのよね……\nまぁ、恋愛に馴染みがないのは認めるけど",
      "startTime": 54.2234722842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんだって\n私と恋愛なんて考えられないでしょ？",
      "startTime": 59.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}